title: Hour 3 - Darren Rovell, Rex Ryan
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Darren Rovell, Rex Ryan
description:
Dan talks to sports business insider Darren Rovell about what Aaron Judge's record breaking homerun will be worth. And former NFL head coach Rex Ryan stops by to break down the NFL season so far and describe what it's like to coach against Bill Belichick.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
